</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   he took the chalice
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                   F
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   and, once more giving thanks
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                                 Gm
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   he gave it to his disciples, saying:
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                               Dm
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   TAKE THIS, ALL OF YOU, AND DRINK FROM IT,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                                   A7
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   FOR THIS IS THE CHALICE OF MY BLOOD,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">        Dm
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   THE BLOOD OF THE NEW AND ETERNAL
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   COVENANT,
